For The Love Of Dom Perignon & Godiva
List.Description:
Sweet on someone? Send an elegantly packaged and thoughtful pairing of two legendary brands - Dom Pérignon and Godiva. Both have set the standard for quality, luxury and heavenly taste. Known for their artful approach to perfecting vintage Champagne, Dom Pérignon is the ideal pairing for Godiva's decadent signature truffles. Often referred to as the cashmere of chocolates, each of these 18 truffles imparts a world of flavor all its own. Think French vanilla, double chocolate raspberry, roasted almond and hazelnut praline. And that's just the beginning...

This gift includes:

  • Dom Pérignon Champagne (750ml)
  • Godiva 18-piece Signature Truffle Assortment
  • Chocolate & Wine gift box




Complimentary Gift Box Options:
Happy Birthday with Dom Perignon & Godiva Truffles
Congratulations with Dom Perignon & Godiva Truffles
Summer Time with Dom Perignon & Godiva Truffles
Wedding Bells with Dom Perignon & Godiva Truffles

Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment

Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.
